parameters:
Priestess Sophia: I didn't understand the reason for the
black request form. I thought it had some special meaning...

Thief Nora: I think it has an important meaning...
Everyone's scent was... really... tense.

Mage Relm: I also felt it, especially Stolge-san seemed
disturbed.

Clea: We just have to complete the requests. It's
unavoidable if we want to take on dragon requests.
Clea: Ect-chan!? Why... are you sick? Are you okay?

Girl Ect: Yeah! I suddenly got better! My body feels
unbelievably light!

Girl Ect: With this, I can help Papa! I might even be able
to help Clea-san and the others too!
Clea: Hehe, I'm looking forward to it.

Girl Ect: Yeah, look forward to it! Oh, I wonder if Papa has
come to the guild?
Clea: Come to think of it, we haven't met yet, have we?

Girl Ect: I see... I wanted to show it to Papa... I'll go
ask Piste-san and the others where he went!
Clea: Yes, we will go on the requests.

Girl Ect: Let's have a meal together with Papa when he comes
back. Promise!

events.name: 王妃カロンへの謁見自動実行

parameters: Cleric Sophia: I apologize for causing you worry.
Sister Eleo: A-Are you feeling alright!?

Cleric Sophia: Yes, perhaps it was a good thing that I
abstained from alcohol for a while?

Mage Relm: Please take this opportunity to moderate
yourself, seriously.

Cleric Sophia: Shall we have this as a celebration for the
recovery?

Thief Nora: This kind of exchange is on hold for a while,
right?
Thief Nora: I-I'm sorry! I said something weird... ugh

Clea: Everyone must have their own goals. Although it's sad
to part ways, it doesn't mean we're saying goodbye forever.

Clea: I am here. If there is anything, I will definitely
cooperate.

Mage Relm: Um... How about meeting again in a month? For
example, it could be an opportunity for information
exchange, you know!?
Cleric Sophia: I don't think there's a need for that.

Clea: Yes, there's no need for that. Let's meet as friends,
not for information exchange.

Clea: Caron-sama will rebuild the house. If you'd like,
please come and visit everyone at that house.

Thief Nora: I'm going out to play! Relm-san, you must
definitely come too!

Mage Relm: W-Well, I guess there's no helping it...! Since
I've been invited as a friend, I will definitely go!

Cleric Sophia: Since we are friends, I will bring a special
wine, hehe.

Mage Relm: Geez, is anything fine as long as it's
drinkable!?

Clea: Although it's a temporary farewell... let's definitely
meet again at this place!
Clea: Take care until we meet again.

Girl Mel: Is the story about the dragon and the great sword
over now?

Bard: It's not an ordinary story... but today, I have a
special song.

Bard: If the song until now was a song of revenge... from
now on, it will be a song of heroes!

Bard: What will Clea become? Who will Clea defeat and become
a hero?

Bard: Just a little longer... please bear with this tone-
deaf bard's song.

events.name: EV021訳ありのオークション1-3

parameters:
Clea: I successfully won the bid for the statue at the
auction.

Stolge of Affection: Could I have delivered it directly to
the client?
Clea: There is something that has been bothering me--

Frustrated Man: Ugh... damn it, I guess it was impossible
for me...

Simos of the Unknown Night: I'll give you credit for having
the guts to pick a fight with me alone, but in order to
prevent similar idiots from appearing, I'll make sure you
die, okay?
Clea: Don't you think we need to hear the reason?

Simos of the Unknown Night: Do you have a problem with my
way of doing things?
Clea: This is my request, so...

Stolge of Affection: Wait, wait, let's stop the fight. You
were the one tailing me, right?

Stolge of Affection: If you're not willing to tell me your
name and reason, there's no point in having a discussion,
right?

Merchant Stora: I am the merchant Stora... The reason is my
son...

Merchant Stora: She looks just like my missing son! That's
why I wanted her so badly... That's why I did something like
this.

Stolge of Affection: Is your son's name by any chance
[Mono]?
Merchant Stora: Why would you do that...!?

Stolge of Affection: Actually, I received a request from a
colleague of your son, who is a member of the Magic Academy.

Stolge of Affection: Depending on the client, it may be
possible for me to hand over the statue to you.

Merchant Stora: P-Please, I beg you! Let me meet that
client!

Stolge of Affection: I will go call Doctor-san, so Clea,
please escort this person to their home.

Simos of Fuchiya Night: Now that we've reached an
understanding... Where do you plan on settling the score for
picking a fight with me?

Stolge of Affection: Would you like to make a bet with me?
It's a game where if the client agrees to hand over the
statue, I will overlook everything.

Simos of Fuchiya Night: So, you're here for your usual
negotiations? Where did the old battle-crazed you go?

Stolge of Affection: Sigh, it's your responsibility and
Agonia's fault...

Stolge of Affection: Well then, please tell me the location
of your home. I will definitely bring your son's colleague
with me.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

events.name: QI『訳ありのオークション』

parameters: Clea: I have finished reporting to the guild leader.

Clea: I don't know what to talk about, even though we're not
parting ways in death or anything.

Thief Nora: I've been so worried...! Whenever I take my eyes
off you for a moment, Clea-san, it feels like you might
disappear.

Thief Nora: Let's continue from that time! It's a charm that
worked well before we fought the dragon!

Thief Nora: Relm-san is an amazing person, but she's also
just a normal person. It's not good to be reckless!

Priestess Sophia: I was completely at the mercy of the
gluttonous Nora-chan. It was more than just troublesome,
hehe, it was fun and amusing...

Priestess Sophia: Please don't go back to being alone, okay?
Just like the world of books, this world is also vast.

Mage Relm: Please drink wine in moderation, as if something
were to happen to your health, we wouldn't be able to meet
anymore...

Mage Relm: Clea-san, please take care of your own body too!
You, the clients, and all of us should be important!

Clea: I was also worried about Nora-san. To someone as weak
as me, Nora-san's strength seemed like bravado.

Clea: Sophia-san, please don't let the past crush you. We
met and will walk together because you are the future.

Clea: I am truly grateful to all of you. I have been able to
stay safe until today thanks to all of you.

Clea: Everyone is moving towards new dreams... that's why...
I tried to send you off... with a smile...

Mage Relm: I won't be able to become an Archmage by the next
time we meet, but I will become an Advanced Sorceress, so
please celebrate for me!

Thief Nora: I will be active in the Emma Mercenary Corps! I
will do my best to assist the leaders!

Priestess Sophia: I will atone for the numerous sins I have
committed under the guidance of Eleo-chan.

Clea: The next time we meet will be at the award ceremony
hosted by King Rex. Let's gather at my house, just like last
time.

Clea: Though it's a temporary farewell... let's definitely
meet again in this place!
Clea: Take care until we meet again.

Clea (Our friends are each heading towards their own new
dreams)

Clea (It's the same as before... just like when we said
goodbye after avenging... )

Clea (Back then, I was in a position to see off my friends
as they moved towards their new dreams...)

Clea (Who am I... even after going through such a journey, I
still haven't found the answer to that)
Clea (No, maybe I just can't [accept] it...)

Clea: The reason should be found within the days we
protected.

Clea: We will definitely find that courage, because our
friends have taught us.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
